AB TO AJAO SHAHAN SHAHE WAFAPLEASE COME BACK OH KING OF LOYALTYEnglish Transliteration
@HujjatELC
Ab To Ajao Shahan Shahe Wafa - Please come back oh King of Loyalty

Shimr Ne Mare Tamache Hai Mere Galon PeJhirkiyan Day Ke Uthaya Hai MujheBaba Ki Laash Pe Rone Na Diya
@HujjatELC
Ab To Ajao Shahan Shahe Wafa - Please come back oh King of Loyalty

Cheen Kar Sab Ki Ridayen Aur Jalaye KhaimeAyse Loota Hai Musalmano NeNa Kiya Aale Muhammad Ka Haya
@HujjatELC
Ab To Ajao Shahan Shahe Wafa - Please come back oh King of Loyalty

Tumko Abbas Ki Taqat Pe Bharosa Tha BohotQaid Hone Se Bachaey TumkoAake Ye Shimr Ne Zainab Se Kaha
@HujjatELC
Ab To Ajao Shahan Shahe Wafa - Please come back oh King of Loyalty

Shaam Jane Kay Liye Qafila Tayyar Hai JoUn Me Ik Raat Ki Byaahi Hai KhariHaathon Se Utra Nahin Range Hina
@HujjatELC
Ab To Ajao Shahan Shahe Wafa - Please come back oh King of Loyalty
